videos.description: Michigan and UCLA have both opened the game hot from the field, including Lonzo Ball who drains the shot from way behind the arc.
videos.headline: Ball continues UCLA's hot shooting with deep 3

videos.description: Aaron Holiday brings in the defense leaving Ike Anigbogu wide open for the massive alley-oop slam to boost UCLA's lead over Michigan.
videos.headline: Huge alley-oop to Anigbogu has UCLA flying

videos.description: 1H (8:19) MICH Duncan Robinson made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: Despite back to back blocks by UCLA, D.Robinson makes the 3 pointer

videos.description: 1H (3:21) MICH Zak Irvin made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Derrick Walton Jr..
videos.headline: Michgian makes their 12th 3 pointer of the 1st half

videos.description: 1H (0:06) UCLA Lonzo Ball made Three Point Jumper.
videos.headline: L. Ball with the deep 3 pointer to tie the game at the half

videos.description: 2H (17:49) UCLA Lonzo Ball made Layup. Assisted by Isaac Hamilton.
videos.headline: Big block by UCLA leads to a layup in transition

videos.description: After a first half of both teams lighting up the scoreboard, Ike Anigbogu lets everyone know he's playing defense in the second half with a vicious rejection for UCLA.
videos.headline: Anigbogu swats shot deep into the crowd

videos.description: UCLA caps off a 7-0 run when Ike Anigbogu gets the rebound and instantly throws the outlet pass to T.J. Leaf for the huge dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Long outlet pass has UCLA running and dunking

videos.description: Breaking down UCLA'S 102-84 victory over Michigan
videos.headline: Breaking down UCLA'S 102-84 victory over Michigan
